<!--
  Clarus the Dogcow — landscape orientation. The same traced silhouette
  rotated 90 degrees clockwise so the dogcow lies on its side, indicating
  landscape page orientation.

  RC18 — bbox-derived translate, this time with the rotation direction
  done correctly. Android's android:rotation on a <group> is screen-CW
  (positive Y down), so a CW 90° rotation around pivot (120,120) sends
  (px, py) → (240 - py, px). For source bbox X∈[4,168] Y∈[4,132] that
  yields rotated bbox X'∈[108, 236], Y'∈[4, 168] with center (172, 86).
  To bring that center to the 240×240 viewport center (120, 120) the
  translate is (120 - 172, 120 - 86) = (−52, +34).

  RC16 had the rotation direction backwards in my head and shipped
  (+52, -34) — exact opposite — which pushed Clarus's body off the
  right edge and head off the top. User saw "only feet visible" (the
  feet, originally at the bottom of the portrait, end up at the LEFT
  in the landscape rotation, so the leftmost part of the rotated bbox
  was the only thing still inside the viewport).
-->
<vector xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:width="240dp"
    android:height="240dp"
    android:viewportWidth="240"
    android:viewportHeight="240">
    <group
        android:pivotX="120.0"
        android:pivotY="120.0"
        android:rotation="90"
        android:translateX="-52.0"
        android:translateY="34.0">
        <path
            android:fillColor="#FF1F1F1F"
            android:pathData="M28,4h8v4h-8zM52,4h12v4h-12zM24,8h4v16h-4zM36,8h4v4h-4zM36,24h4v4h-4zM36,124h4v4h-4zM48,8h4v4h-4zM60,8h4v8h-4zM60,32h4v4h-4zM60,116h4v8h-4zM36,12h12v4h-12zM160,12h4v4h-4zM160,44h4v4h-4zM52,16h8v16h-8zM52,124h8v4h-8zM160,16h8v8h-8zM20,24h4v4h-4zM156,24h4v4h-4zM156,48h4v8h-4zM156,84h4v32h-4zM164,24h4v20h-4zM16,28h4v4h-4zM152,28h4v4h-4zM152,56h4v28h-4zM152,116h4v8h-4zM8,32h8v4h-8zM144,32h8v4h-8zM144,124h8v4h-8zM4,36h4v12h-4zM64,36h8v8h-8zM140,36h4v8h-4zM72,44h68v4h-68zM8,48h32v4h-32zM88,48h44v4h-44zM40,52h4v12h-4zM40,116h4v8h-4zM92,52h40v4h-40zM100,56h24v8h-24zM44,64h8v4h-8zM44,84h8v4h-8zM44,68h16v16h-16zM44,88h4v28h-4zM68,88h56v4h-56zM64,92h4v24h-4zM124,92h8v4h-8zM124,124h8v4h-8zM132,96h4v8h-4zM132,116h4v8h-4zM136,104h4v12h-4zM40,128h12v4h-12zM132,128h12v4h-12z" />
